# Lab: Tach anh tu audio stego bang DWT va key.
# Muc tieu:
# 1. Receiver nhan file stego.wav va secret.key tu sender.
# 2. Receiver sua extract_signal.py va recover_image.py de dien ten file dau vao.
# 3. Receiver tach tin hieu bi mat tu he so tan so cao cua DWT.
# 4. Receiver dung key de dao hoan vi va khoi phuc recovered_secret.png.
# 5. Receiver xac minh recovered_secret.png dung voi anh bi mat ban dau.
